    Generate tibble of demo events

    demo_events.Rd

    emoji and details columns are only generated if the emoji and lorem packages are installed

    Usage

    demo_events(n_events = 5, date_range = NULL, max_duration = 5)

    Arguments

    n_events
    date_range
    max_duration

    Value

    tibble

    Examples

    demo_events(30)
